    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.21.14a"/>
                
                <note type="curatorial">Missouri Collection</note>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        Manderson
                        So Dak
                
                        Oct 11, 1945
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Mr. John G Neihardt</salute>
                    <note type="curatorial">[Chicago, Ill.]</note>
                </opener>
                <p>Will now write and say why is the main reason you've invited me up there as I am anxious to know so please give me a little explanation in the trip also what <unclear>I am</unclear> going to do up there</p>
                
                <p><unclear/> I might bring a little company or an interpreter along</p> 
                
                <p>The Sioux's sure liked the way you gave that speech at that celebration</p>
                
                <p>They sure feel lot of encouragement by you + wish you could help them more in future.</p> 
                
                <p>Well friend try + give me some information thru<si>through</si> 
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.21.14b"/>
                
                    <fw type="authorial">II</fw>
                
                    the <unclear>Supt</unclear> or Agent Roberts so I'll know what to do</p>
                
                <p>Well this is all leading</p> 
                <closer>
                    <salute>best regards + lots of success</salute>
                    <salute>I'm yours respectfully</salute>
                    <signed>Nick Black Elk Sr</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <postscript>
                    <opener><hi rend="caps">P.S.</hi></opener> <p>Ben sends you his best regards also the rest</p>
                </postscript>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">14</fw>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
